/* --- base */
* {
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
height: 100%;
background-color: #fefefe;
}

p {
margin: 0 0 10px;
}

img, input, select, textarea, button {
vertical-align: middle;
}

:focus {outline:none;}
::-moz-focus-inner {border:0;}

input[type="text"], input[type="password"], textarea, .text {
outline: 0;
height: 30px;
padding: 6px;
font-family: "Open Sans","Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;    
border-radius: 2px;    
background-color: #fff;    
color: #666;    
border: 1px solid #D0D1D3;    
box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 0 #efefef;        
width: 100%;
transition: border-color ease-in-out .15s, box-shadow ease-in-out .15s;
}


input[type="text"]:focus, input[type="password"]:focus, textarea:focus, .text:focus {
border-color: #66afe9;
box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.075),0 0 8px rgba(102,175,233,0.6);
}

.text-left { text-align: left; }
.text-center { text-align: center; }
.text-right { text-align: right; }

.normal { font-weight: 400; }
.semibold { font-weight: 600; }
.bold { font-weight: 800; }

/* --- login */
body {
font-family: "Open Sans","Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
color: #555;
font-size: 13px;
line-height: 1.42857143;
}
.full-body {
height: 100%;
width: 100%;
}

#login-body {
height: 100%;
background: url(data:image/png;base64,) repeat #f5f5f5;
}

#login-inset {
position: absolute;
top: 50%;
left: 50%;
}
.login-logo {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.box {
border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
margin-top: 0;
margin-bottom: 25px;
padding: 0;
}
.box.box-shadow {
box-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
border-bottom-color: #ccc;
}
.box .box-content {
  padding: 15px;
  position: relative;
  background-color: #fff;
}
.box .box-footer {
background-color: #f5f5f5;
padding: 8px;
}

.btn {
height: 30px;
cursor: pointer;

font-family: "Open Sans","Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
font-size: 13px;

border-radius: 2px;
background-color: #fff;

color: #666;
border: 1px solid #D0D1D3;
box-shadow: inset 0 -2px 0 0 #efefef;

padding-bottom: 1px;

vertical-align: top;
outline: 0;
}

.btn.disabled {
color: #ccc;
cursor: no-drop;
pointer-events: none;
}

.btn:active {
box-shadow: inset 0 0px 0 0 #efefef, inset 0px 0px 0 2px #fff;

padding-bottom: 0px;
}

.btn-primary {
font-weight: 600;
box-shadow: inset 0 -2px 0 0 #CFE6F5;
}

.cursor-default {
cursor: default;
}

.logo {
  height: 36px;
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
}
.logo-text {
font-size: 26px;
font-weight: 800;
text-shadow: #999 -2px 2px 0px, #999 -2px -2px 0px, #999 2px -2px 0px, #999 2px 2px 0px;
color: #fff;
text-transform: uppercase;
letter-spacing: -2px;
}
.logo-subtext {
text-transform: uppercase;
position: absolute;
bottom: -1px;
right: -4px;
font-size: 12px;
font-weight: 800;
text-shadow: #FFF -1px 1px 0px, #FFF -1px -1px 0px, #FFF 1px -1px 0px, #FFF 1px 1px 0px;
color: #0094F4;
font-family: Lucida console;
opacity: 0.85;
line-height: 1.42857143;
}

a {
color: #4d7496;
text-decoration: none;
outline: 0;
}
a:hover {
text-decoration: underline;
}
a:focus {
color: #2a6496;
text-decoration: underline;
}

.alert {
font-size: 12px;
border-radius: 2px;
color: #666;    
border: 1px solid transparent;
margin-bottom: 15px;
padding: 4px 8px;
text-align: left;
}
.alert.alert-danger {
background-color: #faeaea;
border-color: #fad8d8;
color: #EF3B3B;
}
.alert.alert-warning {
background-color: #F1F2DE;
border-color: #E6EBCC;
color: #8AA942;
}

.close {
position: initial;
top: -2px;
right: -21px;
color: #555;
border: 0;
background-color: transparent;
cursor: pointer;
opacity: 0.4;
float: right;
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 600;
text-shadow: 0 1px 0 #fff;
line-height: 1;
outline: 0;
}
.close:hover {
opacity: 1;
}

.overlay {
position: fixed;
top: 0;
left: 0;
bottom: 0;
right: 0;
background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
z-index: 1050;
}

.signal {
border: 10px solid #777;
border-radius: 18px;
width: 60px;
height: 60px;
position: absolute;
top: 50%;
left: 50%;
margin-top: -30px;
margin-left: -30px;
opacity: 0;

animation: pulsate 1s ease-in-out, spin 2s ease-in-out;
animation-iteration-count: infinite;
}

@keyframes pulsate {
0% {
transform: scale(.1);
opacity: 0;
}
50% {
opacity: 1;
}
100% {
transform: scale(1.2);
opacity: 0;
}
}

@keyframes spin {
0% {
transform:rotate(0deg);
}
50% {
transform:rotate(180deg);
}
100% {
transform:rotate(360deg);
}
}

.dot {
width: 20px;
height: 20px;
position: absolute;
top: 50%;
left: 50%;
border: 5px solid #777;
margin-left: -10px;
margin-top: -10px;
border-radius: 5px;
animation: rspin 2s ease-in;
animation-iteration-count: infinite;
opacity: 1;
}

@keyframes rspin {
0% {
transform:rotate(360deg);
opacity: 1;
}
50% {
transform:rotate(180deg);
opacity: 0.2;
}
100% {
transform:rotate(0deg);
opacity: 1;
}
}

      if(s[0]()) {
        _.loadStack.splice(i, 1);
        s[1]();
      }
    });
    
    if(!_.loadStack.length) {
      clearInterval(i);
    }
    
  }, 25);
  
};

  $(function() {

  });
  
});
